reviewText: I love lifetime movies they shouls have more to buy. Then I would buy them if they were the ones that I like!

This Is For The Peeps Who Wanted To Know What Movies Are On This 6 Pack.. (i gave it 4 stars just cause i haven't watched these movies)

1. Trial by Media

2. Sex & Mrs. X

3. Another Woman's Husband

4. Where the Truth Lies

5. Prison of Secrets

6. The Abduction

I am a huge fan or Lifetime tv movies but about this is they want you to pay 90 dollars and they don't tell you what the movies are in this six pack. I love lifetime movies but I would like to know what the movies are if I am going to pull out 90 bucks.
